PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of TRACEY BAKKELI, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Shawn A. Murphy, who has resigned.
